headline: Black Duck Announces MSSP Agreement with Accenture, Combining World-Class Application Security Technology and Services
summary: Black Duck®, the leader in AI-powered application security, today announced it has signed a managed security service provider (MSSP) agreement with Accenture. This strategic agreement combines Black Duck's world-class application security technology with Accenture's expertise and global reach, enhancing the delivery of comprehensive and cutting-edge security solutions to clients worldwide.
